'''[[Tele2 Arena]]''' is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Stockholm Globe City]], located in [[Johanneshov]], just south of [[Stockholm City Centre]], [[Sweden]], that was open in July 2013. The following is a complete list of all events that have been or will be held at the arena. In addition, the stadium is used as the home venue of the football teams [[Djurgårdens IF Fotboll|Djurgårdens IF]] and [[Hammarby IF]].
