{{Orphan|date=February 2018}}

'''Skredkommissionen''' (Swedish for "landslide commission") was a commission established in 1988 to research, develop and provide information about landslides in Swedish. It was disbanded in 1996.<ref name=Skredrapp>{{cite web |url=http://www.swedgeo.se/sv/kunskapscentrum/publikationsserier/i-samverkan-med-andra/skredkommissionen/ |title=Skredkommissionens rapporter |last= |first= |date=April 7, 2016 |website=Swedgeo.se |publisher= |access-date=July 23, 2017|language=Swedish |quote=}}</ref> It was part of [[Ingenjörsvetenskapsakademien]].<ref name=Skredrapp/> [[Curt Fredén]] was a member.<ref name=Skredrapp/>

